'''肉凍''' (aspic) 是一種[[菜餚|菜餚]]，做法是將[[清湯|清湯]]加工為類似[[果凍|果凍]]的形狀，並在其中鑲入肉塊、蔬菜、水果等食物。肉凍和中餐[[水晶餚肉|水晶餚肉]]的做法相似。肉凍的詳細配方在中世紀時就已經出現<ref>{{Cite book|last= Scully|first=Terence|authorlink=|title=The viandier of Taillevent: an edition of all extant manuscripts|publisher=University of Ottawa Press|date=January 1, 1988|location=Ottawa, Ontario|pages=270|url=|doi =|id=|isbn=978-0-7766-0174-8}}</ref>。20世紀初期，肉凍開始在[[美國|美國]]流行<ref name="oxfordbook">{{Cite book|last = Smith| first = Andrew| authorlink = | title = The Oxford Companion to American Food and Drink| publisher = Oxford University Press| date = March 2007| location =New York, New York| pages = 514, 292| url =| doi =| id =| isbn =0-19-530796-8}}</ref>{{rp|514}}。
